script.name: !ship.cmd.trade.dist.std
script.sourceplaintext:
[THIS] ->set command: COMMAND_TRADE_DISTRIBUTE
$current.pos = 0 $max.runs = size of array $a.runArray
while [THIS] -> exists @ = wait randomly from 10000 to 20000 ms
$destination.id = $current.pos $destination.array = $a.runArray[$current.pos] $destination = $destination.array[0] inc $current.pos =
$run.text = sprintf: fmt='%s/%s', $current.pos, $max.runs, null, null, null $run.text = change datatype[COMMAND_TRADE_DISTRIBUTE] to DATATYPE_INT $run.text = read text: page=2010 id=$run.text $run.text = sprintf: fmt='%s (%s/%s)', $run.text, $current.pos, $max.runs, null, null [THIS] ->set command display override: text=$run.text
do if $current.pos >= $max.runs $current.pos = 0
$dest.sector = $destination -> get sector
* now dock at the target $actual.destination = $destination while $destination != [DOCKEDAT] * if auto jump, load enogh energy cells if possible @ = [THIS] -> call script !lib.trade.home.refuel : destination station=$destination One Way?=[TRUE] Move Home=[FALSE]
$text = sprintf: pageid=6020 textid=2077, $destination, null, null, null, null [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$text [THIS] ->set destination to $destination if [THIS] -> is of class Ship if $destination -> is docking possible of [THIS] @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetostation : station=$destination else if $destination -> is docked $actual.destination = $destination $destination = $destination -> is docked @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetostation : station=$destination else do if [THIS] -> is docked @ = [THIS] -> call script !move.undock :
if [THIS] -> has same environment as $destination $dist = get distance between [THIS] and $destination do if $dist <= 5000 break else if [THIS] -> is in same sector as $destination do if $destination -> is docked @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.idle.timeout : timeout in sec=60 wait while docked=[TRUE] end @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetoobject : Target=$destination Range=3000 end else @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script !move.movetostation : station=$destination end if $ret == FLRET_NOPATH if [OWNER] == Player $this.code = [THIS] -> get ID code if not [DOCKEDAT] -> exists $read.text = sprintf: pageid=6020 textid=2125, [THIS], $destination, [THIS], $this.code, null send incoming message $read.text to player: type:[Log.Alert], display it=[FALSE] return $ret else $docked.owner = [DOCKEDAT] -> get owner race if $docked.owner != Player $read.text = sprintf: pageid=6020 textid=2125, [THIS], $destination, [THIS], $this.code, null send incoming message $read.text to player: type:[Log.Alert], display it=[FALSE] return $ret end end end
$read.text = read text: page=6020 id=2123 [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$read.text
@ = wait randomly from 30000 to 60000 ms end @ = wait 2000 ms end
[THIS] ->set destination to null $next.destination = $a.runArray[$current.pos][0] $destination = $actual.destination
* do all the commands $cmd.table = table alloc $table = $destination.array[1] $ware = get next key: table=$table key=null while $ware $cmd.array = array alloc: size=4 $array = $table[$ware] $cmd.array[0] = $array[0] $cmd.array[1] = $array[1] $cmd.array[2] = $array[2] $cmd.array[3] = $array[3] $cmd.table[$ware] = $cmd.array $ware = get next key: table=$table key=$ware end
* dump wares first $read.text = read text: page=6020 id=2126 [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$read.text
if $cmd.table[-1] $wait = $cmd.table[-1][2] $ship.wares = [THIS] ->get wares table: include equipped=[FALSE] if $ship.wares while size of table $ship.wares $ware = get next key: table=$ship.wares key=null while $ware $amt = $ship.wares[$ware] $price = get average price of ware $ware gosub sub.UnloadWare $ware = get next key: table=$ship.wares key=$ware end
skip if $wait break $ship.wares = [THIS] ->get wares table: include equipped=[FALSE] skip if $ship.wares break @ = wait 5000 ms end end end
@ = wait 1000 ms
* unload any wares while size of table $cmd.table $found.any = [FALSE] $ware = get next key: table=$cmd.table key=null while $ware $next.ware = get next key: table=$cmd.table key=$ware $cmd = $cmd.table[$ware][0] $amt = $cmd.table[$ware][1] $wait = $cmd.table[$ware][2] $price = $cmd.table[$ware][3]
if $cmd == 'cmd.unload' $found.any = [TRUE] $dest.amt = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay do if $dest.amt < $amt $amt = $dest.amt gosub sub.UnloadWare if $wait AND $amt > $done.amt $amt = $amt - $done.amt $cmd.table[$ware][1] = $amt else remove key $ware from table $cmd.table end
else if $cmd == 'cmd.stock' $found.any = [TRUE] $this.amt = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $dest.amt = $destination -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $need.amt = $amt - $dest.amt
if $need.amt <= 0 OR $this.amt < 0 remove key $ware from table $cmd.table else $need.amt = get minimum, $need.amt, $this.amt, null, null, null $amt = $need.amt gosub sub.UnloadWare if not $wait AND $need.amt > $done.amt remove key $ware from table $cmd.table end end else if $cmd == 'cmd.dump' remove key $ware from table $cmd.table end $ware = $next.ware end
skip if $found.any break @ = wait randomly from 20000 to 30000 ms end @ = wait 1000 ms
* finally, load any wares $read.text = read text: page=6020 id=2079 [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$read.text
@ = [THIS] -> call script !lib.trade.home.refuel : destination station=$next.destination One Way?=[TRUE] Move Home=[FALSE]
while size of table $cmd.table $ware = get next key: table=$cmd.table key=null while $ware $next.ware = get next key: table=$cmd.table key=$ware $cmd = $cmd.table[$ware][0] $amt = $cmd.table[$ware][1] $wait = $cmd.table[$ware][2] $price = $cmd.table[$ware][3] skip if $price $price = get average price of ware $ware
if $cmd == 'cmd.load' $dest.amt = $destination -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay do if $dest.amt < $amt $amt = $dest.amt gosub sub.LoadWare $amt = $cmd.table[$ware][1] $this.free = [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay if $wait AND $amt > $done.amt AND $this.free > 0 $amt = $amt - $done.amt $cmd.table[$ware][1] = $amt else remove key $ware from table $cmd.table end
else if $cmd == 'cmd.fill' $this.amt = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay if $ware == Energy Cells if [THIS] -> get true amount of ware Jumpdrive in cargo bay if [THIS] -> is autojump activated $next.dest.sector = $next.destination -> get sector $needed.energy = [THIS] -> needed jump drive energy for jump to sector $next.dest.sector $this.amt = $this.amt - $needed.energy end end end
$need.amt = $amt - $this.amt if $need.amt <= 0 remove key $ware from table $cmd.table else $amt = $need.amt $dest.amt = $destination -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay do if $dest.amt < $amt $amt = $dest.amt gosub sub.LoadWare $this.free = [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay if not $wait AND $need.amt > $done.amt AND $this.free > 0 remove key $ware from table $cmd.table end end
else if $cmd == 'cmd.unload' remove key $ware from table $cmd.table else if $cmd == 'cmd.stock' remove key $ware from table $cmd.table else if $cmd == 'cmd.dump' remove key $ware from table $cmd.table end
$ware = $next.ware end @ = wait randomly from 20000 to 30000 ms end
@ = wait 1000 ms $read.text = read text: page=6020 id=2078 [THIS] ->set command extra display override: text=$read.text
end return null
sub.LoadWare: $done.amt = 0 if ! [DOCKEDAT] OR [DOCKEDAT] != $destination if $destination -> is of class Ship $has.transporter = [FALSE] if [DOCKEDAT] $has.transporter = [TRUE] else do if [THIS] -> get volume of ware Transporter Device in cargo bay $has.transporter = [TRUE] do if $destination -> get volume of ware Transporter Device in cargo bay $has.transporter = [TRUE] end if $has.transporter if $destination -> can transport ware $ware $this.free = [THIS] -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $ship.amt = $destination -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay do if $amt > $this.free $amt = $this.free if $amt > $ship.amt $negative = - $ship.amt else $negative = - $amt end $transfered = $destination -> add $negative units of $ware $done.amt = - $transfered if $done.amt > 0 = [THIS] -> add $done.amt units of $ware end end end end else $docked.owner = [DOCKEDAT] -> get owner race if $docked.owner == [OWNER] $done.amt = [THIS] ->load $amt units of $ware, ignore minimum=[FALSE] else $done.amt = [THIS] -> buy $amt units of $ware to a max. price of $price Cr end end endsub
sub.GetProperWareCount: $table.resupply = [THIS] ->get resupply table $this.amt = [THIS] -> get true amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $ware.resupply = $table.resupply[$ware] do if $ware.resupply > 0 $this.amt = $this.amt - $ware.resupply do if $this.amt <= 0 $this.amt = 0 endsub
sub.UnloadWare: $done.amt = 0 if ! [DOCKEDAT] OR [DOCKEDAT] != $destination if $destination -> is of class Ship $has.transporter = [FALSE] if [DOCKEDAT] $has.transporter = [TRUE] else do if [THIS] -> get volume of ware Transporter Device in cargo bay $has.transporter = [TRUE] do if $destination -> get volume of ware Transporter Device in cargo bay $has.transporter = [TRUE] end if $has.transporter if $destination -> can transport ware $ware $ship.free = $destination -> get free amount of ware $ware in cargo bay gosub sub.GetProperWareCount do if $amt > $this.amt $amt = $this.amt if $amt > $ship.free $transfered = $destination -> add $ship.free units of $ware else $transfered = $destination -> add $amt units of $ware end $done.amt = $transfered if $transfered > 0 $transfered = - $transfered = [THIS] -> add $transfered units of $ware end end end end else $docked.owner = [DOCKEDAT] -> get owner race if $docked.owner == [OWNER] if $docked.owner == Player if [DOCKEDAT] -> is of class Dock skip if [DOCKEDAT] -> trades with ware $ware [DOCKEDAT] ->add product to factory or dock: $ware end end gosub sub.GetProperWareCount do if $amt > $this.amt $amt = $this.amt $done.amt = [THIS] -> unload $amt units of $ware else gosub sub.GetProperWareCount do if $amt > $this.amt $amt = $this.amt $ware.price = [DOCKEDAT] -> get price of ware $ware if $ware.price >= $price $done.amt = [THIS] -> sell $amt units of $ware else $done.amt = 0 end end end endsub return null
